    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pasta is cooked, add it to the pan with the sauce,<strong> </strong>a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>goats' cheese, chorizo & spinach tortiglioni</strong></p>",
