    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>goats' cheese, chorizo & spinach tortiglioni</strong> with the <strong>remaining goats' cheese</strong> sprinkled over the top</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped basil</strong> and <strong>remaining dried chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
